Users:
- id (unique identifier)
- username
- email
- password (hashed)
- role (admin, user, etc.)

Questions:
- id (unique identifier)
- title
- body
- user_id (reference to the user who asked the question)
- tags (list of tags associated with the question)
- created_at
- updated_at

Answers:
- id (unique identifier)
- body
- user_id (reference to the user who provided the answer)
- question_id (reference to the question the answer belongs to)
- created_at
- updated_at

Tags:
- id (unique identifier)
- name
